locality: Rift Valley, Laikipia, Mpala Research Centre

33.4 km from Mgori on rd to Nduamughanga. Slightly rolling landscape, mostly sandy loams. Scrubby cover just outside miombo woodland, mostly 3-6 m but emergents to 15 m; mostly Combretum, also Grewia, Strophanthus eminii, Cassia, Acacia tortilis.
